nodes.text: CT-12/74, also known as Seefor, was a clone trooper in the Galactic Republic's squad on Ord Cestus during the Clone Wars. He was a communications expert.

Along with Advanced Recon Commando Captain Nate, and fellow clone troopers Forry and Sirty, Seefor attempted to stop Captain Nate from violating their code by not following the instructions that Generals Kenobi and Fisto gave them.
